article_title: Support for Hamas rises in the West Bank.
sentence: The  UN  says  here  in  the  West  Bank,  271  Palestinians,  including  69  children,  have  been  killed  since  Hamas's  7  October  attack  -  almost  all  of  these  have  been  killed  by  Israeli  forces.
